title: ITIL V3 (Books)
description:
ITIL Lifecycle Publication Suite (ITILv3 - Complete Library)

ITIL Version 3 (ITILv3) - the ITIL Service Lifecycle Publication Suite

Represents an important evolutionary step in the life of ITIL. 

See how the refresh has transformed the guidance from providing a great service to being the most innovative and best in class. At the same time, the interface between old and new approaches is seamless.
